Lagos –  Cruel photos have surfaced showing the moment parents of a little boy tied him to the ceiling before pouring grounded pepper on his face. Facebook user, identified as Prince Adefila Sunday shared the photos urging Nigerians to help the little boy identified as Daniel Ogunbona who is currently being assaulted and maltreated by his parents. Bamidele disclosed that the incident happened at no. 35 Komumo Road, Alimosho, Iyana Ipaja, Lagos. Nigerians have taken to social media to react to the sad incident. While some are expressing their resentment towards the brutal act, others have sworn to make sure the young boy gets justice. Source